Currently there isn't a way to view the total amount of projects or repositories that are present in Stash via the User Interface. 

You can however get the total amount of projects through the use of the below REST end point with GET;

- https://developer.atlassian.com/static/rest/stash/3.10.2/stash-rest.html#idp7392

